nk?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_772226_0&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHLTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=00bfb89a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Farticle%2F2_772226_0&h=f9d3a066\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/article/2_772226_0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第四波武漢肺炎疫情仍然持續，政府宣佈延長一系列防疫措施，包括二人限聚令及晚市禁堂食等至本月二十日，入夜後街道更顯冷清。  不過，本刊記者發現有火鍋店無視防疫措施，公然違規，晚上如常開門做生意，而光顧的食客亦「非常醒目」在後巷出入，掩人耳目。<br />\n<br />\n上月29號晚上八時許，位於佐敦偉晴街的「<strong><span class=\"x-large\">淘園刺身火鍋館</span></strong>」大閘落下，以為已停業，其實火鍋館很蠱惑，只做熟客生意。食客只要先訂枱，就有職員帶路行後巷經過廚房入餐廳。記者向後門職員訛稱，指有朋友在內，職員便放行。......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搵過好似冇人講 所以我講<br />\n佐敦油麻地大爆發 佢係咪源頭？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/discover.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d26e0ed8eb9de99c9602fbca856939e7945e8542","tid":2369961,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:35:00.000Z","msg":"應付壹傳媒狗KLN方法<br />\n唔使覆<br />\n負評<br />\n由佢沉"},{"pid":"fe1ef949aed4e66e072e1737ed88a5e95b9cb960","tid":2369961,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:42:32.000Z","msg":"30:08 乜哩顏色口罩都係一樣, 無分別 <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CYZs_Wg0wls?t=1808\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCYZs_Wg0wls%3Ft%3D1808&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHLTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=153aa81d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CYZs_Wg0wls?t=1808</a>"},{"pid":"d7e96ebd252116d3ea8c3286d89344c4412064ad","tid":2369961,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fe1ef949aed4e66e072e1737ed88a5e95b9cb960","tid":2369961,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-18T07:42:32.000Z","msg":"30:08 乜哩顏色口罩都係一樣, 無分別 <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CYZs_Wg0wls?t=1808\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCYZs_Wg0wls%3Ft%3D1808&d=yNoj9Y4wDskJCdIfGyfDHLTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=153aa81d\